column3: A child of man enters Anyx Trine... Interesting...
What kind of place is this?
I am Sehn Y Toh. My brothers and sisters are as one under Hraesvelgr. We purge this place of all who bear us ill will.
We seek quiet and calm. Those who deny us will be met with fangs and claws.
Heed me, mortal. Should you disturb the peace of our home, we will know...
Anyx Trine is the work of man in ages past.
But man has long forgotten the fruits of his labor.
The origins of Anyx Trine are not our concern. These grounds are silent. They suit our needs. Anyx Trine is our home now.
